org.azyva.dragom.execcontext.plugin

Interface ExecContextPlugin

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CredentialStorePlugin, EventPlugin, RuntimePropertiesPlugin, UserInteractionCallbackPlugin, WorkspacePlugin

    public interface ExecContextPlugin
    Marker interface for ExecContext plugins.

    There is no predefined method that an ExecContextPlugin must implement. But we introduce a specific type for ExecContext plugins to enforce type safety.

    ExecContextPlugin's that need to be aware of tool life cycle must also implement ToolLifeCycleExecContextPlugin.

    Author:
    David Raymond
